name: Crypto Dealer's Story II - Negative 4 - The Internet God
description: It was very interesting when I found the Internet God. I imagined s/he was just like that, feline, but I didn't know s/he smoked pot either. The God of the Internet was sick and had an immense difficulty in assuming his/her own behavior. S/he was the one who released the photo of my threesome with Liberty and the Redeemer. S/he insists it was the dog, but I know the Cat very well. I lived in his/her castle, isolated in a Cryptovoxels space, for many days, or months, or years... I'm not quite sure of the time, but I know that there were at least 12500 joints. As sick as the Cat is and as much as s/he has imprisoned me to pet him/her, I still like him/her a lot and supply him/her monthly with marijuana; nevertheless, I still don't know if s/he is a boy or a girl.
